    <string name="about_coming_features_title">Coming Features (Next 1–2 Releases)</string>
    <string name="about_coming_features_list">- In-app purchases, including premium subscription to remove most ads\n- In-game store to buy content\n- Selectable tabletop backgrounds\n- Selectable card backs and card faces\n- Cool animations\n- Sound effects\n- Theme packs\n- And more</string>
